<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10147828>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8 A1–A3. Simplexollata carocollata (Lamarck, 1822), NHMW 1856/0035/0358a, Saucats (France), Burdigalian. B1– B3. Simplexollata carocollata (Lamarck, 1822), NHMW 1856/0035/0358b, Saucats (France), Burdigalian. C1–C3. Simplexollata carocollata (Lamarck, 1822), NHMW 1850/0018/0115, Léognan (France), Burdigalian. D1–D3. Simplexollata gratteloupi (d’Orbigny, 1852), MNHN.F.J05823, Saint-Jean-de-Marsacq (France), Late Burdigalian." ;
